background_repeat=\"repeat\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Erick Minor - Certs\" image=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/erick-minor.jpg\" background_layout=\"dark\" _builder_version=\"3.0.101\" custom_css_blurb_title=\"color: #b92025 !important;\" /][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"2_3\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Erick Minor\" background_layout=\"dark\" _builder_version=\"3.0.101\" header_font=\"Montserrat|700|||||||\" header_font_size=\"36px\" header_letter_spacing=\"5px\" custom_margin=\"||0px|\"]\r\n\r\n<h1>Erick Minor</h1>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text admin_label=\"FOUNDER &amp; CEO, STRENGTH STUDIO INC.\" module_class=\"redtxt\" _builder_version=\"3.0.101\" text_font=\"||||||||\" header_font=\"||||||||\" header_2_font=\"||||||||\" header_4_font=\"Montserrat|700|||||||\" header_4_font_size=\"24px\" header_4_letter_spacing=\"3px\"]\r\n\r\n<h4>FOUNDER &amp; CEO, STRENGTH STUDIO INC.</h4>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Erick Minor Bio\" background_layout=\"dark\" _builder_version=\"3.0.101\" text_font=\"Montserrat||||||||\" text_font_size=\"17px\"]\r\n\r\nPersonal trainer and strength coach, Erick Minor, is a leading expert in the fields of athletic preparation, muscle hypertrophy, and fat loss. Erick became interested in exercise at the age of 18 when he enlisted in the U.S. Air Force. HIs love of strength training led him to compete in powerlifting, bodybuilding, and strongman. His experience as an athlete and coach has enhanced his ability to achieve optimal results for his clients.\r\n<br/>\r\nErick has mastered the art of designing strength programs and nutritional strategies that ensure rapid results. This integrated approach allows his clients to lose fat, gain muscle, reduce injury potential, and improve athletic performance in a safe and efficient manner. Along with training many fitness enthusiasts and physique athletes, Erick has trained collegiate, Olympic and professional athletes from several sports including; track and field, MLB, MMA, football, and golf.\r\n<br/>\r\nWith over 22 years of practical experience in strength training, and an extensive background in kinesiology, nutrition, and supplementation; Erick is recognized as an innovator in the fitness industry.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row background_color=\"#c7c7c7\" _builder_version=\"3.0.101\" background_size=\"initial\" background_position=\"top_left\" background_repeat=\"repeat\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Certifications\" _builder_version=\"3.0.101\" header_font=\"Montserrat|700|||||||\" header_text_align=\"center\" header_font_size=\"24px\" header_text_color=\"#ae1f23\" background_layout=\"light\" header_letter_spacing=\"3px\"]\r\n\r\n<h1>Certifications</h1>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row background_color=\"#c7c7c7\" _builder_version=\"3.0.101\" background_size=\"initial\" background_position=\"top_left\" background_repeat=\"repeat\" custom_css_main_element=\"padding: 10px 100px 25px 100px !important;\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Certified Personal Trainer (ACE, NASM)\" background_layout=\"dark\" _builder_version=\"3.0.101\" text_font=\"Montserrat|700||on|||||\" text_font_size=\"16px\" text_line_height=\"1.2em\" header_font=\"Montserrat|700|||||||\" header_text_align=\"center\" header_font_size=\"24px\" header_text_color=\"#ae1f23\" background_color=\"#323232\" text_orientation=\"center\" custom_padding=\"10px||10px|\"]\r\n\r\nCertified<br/>Personal Trainer<br/>(ACE, NASM)\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Poliquin Biosignature Practitioner Level 2\" background_layout=\"dark\" _builder_version=\"3.0.101\" text_font=\"Montserrat|700||on|||||\" text_font_size=\"16px\" text_line_height=\"1.2em\" header_font=\"Montserrat|700|||||||\" header_text_align=\"center\" header_font_size=\"24px\" header_text_color=\"#ae1f23\" background_color=\"#323232\" text_orientation=\"center\" c